---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="博文专栏 - 道奎">
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-tao-gold text-center mb-12">博文专栏</h1>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- 示例文章卡片 -->
      <article class="bg-tao-gray/50 border border-tao-gold/20 rounded-lg p-6 card-enter hover:border-tao-gold/50 transition-all gold-glow">
        <div class="text-tao-cyan text-xs mb-2">道教文化 · 2026-07-07</div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-tao-gold mb-3">《道德经》第一章解读</h2>
        <p class="text-tao-light/70 text-sm mb-4">道可道，非常道。名可名，非常名。无名天地之始，有名万物之母...</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-tao-cyan hover:text-tao-gold text-sm">阅读全文 →</a>
      </article>
      
      <article class="bg-tao-gray/50 border border-tao-gold/20 rounded-lg p-6 card-enter hover:border-tao-gold/50 transition-all gold-glow" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
        <div class="text-tao-cyan text-xs mb-2">周易 · 2026-07-06</div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-tao-gold mb-3">乾卦：元亨利贞</h2>
        <p class="text-tao-light/70 text-sm mb-4">乾为天，健也。刚健中正，自强不息。初九：潜龙勿用...</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-tao-cyan hover:text-tao-gold text-sm">阅读全文 →</a>
      </article>
      
      <article class="bg-tao-gray/50 border border-tao-gold/20 rounded-lg p-6 card-enter hover:border-tao-gold/50 transition-all gold-glow" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
        <div class="text-tao-cyan text-xs mb-2">术数 · 2026-07-05</div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-tao-gold mb-3">八字入门：天干地支详解</h2>
        <p class="text-tao-light/70 text-sm mb-4">十天干：甲乙丙丁戊己庚辛壬癸。十二地支：子丑寅卯辰巳午未申酉戌亥...</p>
        <a href="#" class="text-tao-cyan hover:text-tao-gold text-sm">阅读全文 →</a>
      </article>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 加载更多 -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <button class="px-6 py-2 border border-tao-gold/50 rounded-lg text-tao-gold hover:bg-tao-gold/10 transition-all">
        加载更多
      </button>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
